                    Use TypeScript to Develop Vue.js Web Applications
                    Course Notes


1 - Write a Vue Component as a Class in TypeScript
Clone the starter repo from the course
  - Then cd into the folder and run npm install
Example Syntax
  // Hello.vue component
  <template>
    <div class="hello">
      <h1>{{ fullMessage }}</h1>
      <button @click="clicked">Click</button>
    </div>
  </template>
  
  <script lang="ts">
    export default {
    
    }
  </script>

